highlights.text: Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Imphal. “Ghost” is the highest at #8.
“Dandelions” by Ruth B. has been on Top Songs Imphal the longest, at 56 weeks straight.
“Rasiya” by Pritam, Shreya Ghoshal, and TUSHAR JOSHI is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Imphal, up 22 spots at #78.
“My Mind & Me” by Selena Gomez is the highest new entry on Top Songs Imphal at #22.
